[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "久方ぶりの我が地元……\n景色も雰囲気も何も変わっておらぬな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01293",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "従者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お待ちしておりました、鬼門様",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_719_504_01294",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "……どうも、ご無沙汰しております。\nお迎え感謝いたしまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01295",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "従者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "当主様がお待ちです",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_719_504_01296",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "……うむ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01297",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "父上……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01298",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "おお……戻ったか、鬼門",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01299",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "ご加減はいかがでございますか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01300",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "余計な気遣いはいらぬ。\n……それより、お前を呼んだ理由、分かっておるな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01301",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "……はい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01302",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "断りなく家を飛び出し、長らく便りも寄こさず……\nご迷惑をおかけいたしました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01303",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "それはもうよい。それで、お前の意志はどうなのだ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01304",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "すでに家を継ぐ覚悟はできておりまする。\n次期当主として、再び忍びの修行に打ち込み――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01305",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お前は、何かやるべきことがあって、\n家を出ていたのではなかったのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01306",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "それは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01307",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "それは、もう終わった話でございまする。\n父上が気にされるようなことでは……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01308",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……仲間に恵まれ、大きな舞台に立ち、\nようやく活動が軌道に乗り始めていた。それなのにか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01309",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "え……？　父上がなぜそれを……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01310",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お前の動向は、家の者に見張らせていた。\n初めはすぐにでも連れ戻すつもりだったのだがな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01311",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "お前は我らのような古い世代とは違う、\n新たな忍びの形を模索しようとしていた。そうだろう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01312",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "……はい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01313",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "この争いのない太平の世にあって、かつての\n忍びというものは役目を終えたと思っておりました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01314",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "ならばこの忍術はなんのために使えばよいのか……\nそこで行きついたのがアイドルの道でございまする",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01315",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ならば、なぜそれを捨てようとする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01316",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "そ、それはどういう……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01317",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "我が家の伝統とは、あくまで技術の継承のためのもの。\nそれをどう使うかは、次期当主であるお前が決めるのだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01318",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "当然、継承のための修行や家の仕事はやってもらう。\nだが、それと両立できるのであれば……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01319",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "アイドルの道を、諦める必要などない",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01320",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "父上……！　そ、それはまことにございますか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01321",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "従者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "当主様は、密かに鬼門様の活動を\n応援なさっていたのですよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_719_504_01322",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "従者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "舞台に上がる際には、我々に動画を撮影させたりも……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_719_504_01323",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "そうなのですか……！？　いや、それはちょっと\nマナー的にどうかと思いまするが……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01324",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ごほん！　ごほん！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01325",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "従者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "とはいえ、直接伝えるのも恥ずかしかったのでしょう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_719_504_01326",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "従者",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "よく手紙をしたためては、\nわざわざ偽名を使ってまで送っていらっしゃいました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_719_504_01327",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "――っ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01328",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "父上だったのですね……\n拙者の心を、ずっと支えてくださっていたのは",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01329",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "ありがとうございまする……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01330",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "父親",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "して、どうする？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_638_504_01331",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "8669110150163868408",
		"text": "……忍びも、アイドルも。\nどちらも背負ってみせましょうぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_01332",
		"still_path_hash": "7367252523135796624",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]